VERSION HISTORY
================

v ???
! debug: disabled the winapi window
! debug: new class structure
! axRand: moved the default axRand methods into a class
+ extern/isaac - crypto-safe random number generator
* axUtils: fixed a -fPIC / axCPUID issue
* ladspa: added hints and override values for the parameters
??

v0.1.1a - 290610
* fixed some issue with 64bit builds
* axRand: use simplistic axRand() by default, more complicated prngs are enabled
  with a flag.
  
v0.1.1 - 230610
+ ladspa: added support for ladspa (win32 & linux)
+ extern/mverb: added open source (gpl) reverb engine by martin eastwood
+ ports: added mverb plugin port
+ ports: added sstillwell_eventhorizon port
+ compile: added timestamp option (-ts)
+ compile: added option to disable gui (-nogui)
+ compile: added the option to pass additional flags to the compiler
* vst: fixed support for older vst hosts
* vst: fixed blank presets in energyxt
* vst: fixed crash if no programs  
